        Constructor
        Parameters:
        maxVideoRecordingTime - If recording a video, max recording time. (IN SECONDS! NOT IN MILLISECONDS!)
        nameOfFile - The name of the file
        pathToFile - The path to the file
        shouldUploadPhoto - Boolean, should the photo be uploaded or not
        shouldDeletePhotoAfter - Boolean, should the photo be deleted or not afterwards
        useDefaultToFrontFacingCamera - Boolean, should the camera default to the front facing camera or not
        alertDialog - Alert dialog. If none selected, default one (PGMacCustom SVG) will be selected
        webImageUrlToDownload - The web imageURL String if included
        videoExtension - The video extension format CameraUtilities.SupportedVideoFileExtensions
        photoExtension - The photo extension format CameraUtilities.SupportedPhotoFileExtensions
